Apart from his legendary career, a great advocate of civil rights, environmental protection and independent cinema, an opponent of Hollywood's drifting away, is now passing away.
We have often seen him standing with his foot in bowls full of vinaigrette, in sauces, pastries or other foods, and considered this to be quite tasteless, although we found it funny at the beginning.
